===Etymology===
The etymology is uncertain; older forms are {{term|Madraspatan|lang=en}}, {{term|Madraspatanam|lang=en}}, and {{term|Madraspattinam|lang=en}}, the final element being from {{etyl|sa}} {{term|पत्तन|tr=pattana||village, city|lang=sa|sc=Deva}}{{fact}}. It is possible that ''Madras'' is from {{etyl|ar}} {{term|مدرسة|tr=madrásah||college|lang=ar|sc=Arab}}, from {{term|درس|tr=dárasa||to learn, to study|sc=Arab|lang=ar}}.

